 detailed design stage but suggest </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">that </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">potential savings</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> could have been made</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> on </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">the HA’s scheme</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 30pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-30pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">2.5</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">In summary, KCC has identified overall cost savings on </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">the HA scheme through a review of:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 30pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-30pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 8.68pt; padding-left:9.32pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">c</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">alculation of risk allowance; </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 8.68pt; padding-left:9.32pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">risks associated with land costs;</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 8.68pt; padding-left:9.32pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">phasing and splitting of utilities works;</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 8.68pt; padding-left:9.32pt; text-align:justify; text-inden